title: Campaigners march in support of welcoming migrants
text:
Marchers in Cambridge Credit: ITV Anglia Around 300 people are marching in Cambridge in support of welcoming migrants to the city.
The march began at Parkers Piece at 11am.
People are marching through Cambridge in support of welcoming refugees to the city Credit: ITV Anglia Last updated Sat 10 Oct 2015 Read more 2 updates March for refugees World Cambridgeshire Cambridge
